# Core Features

## 1. Shared Clipboard

A central clipboard accessible from any browser.

Features

* Save text
* Copy text
* Edit text
* Delete text
* Pin important items
* Search clipboard history
* Copy to system clipboard using Clipboard API
* Display creation timestamp
* Display device name

Supported Content

* Plain text
* URLs
* Code
* JSON
* XML
* Markdown
* SQL queries
* Terminal commands

Clipboard history should be ordered newest first.

---

## 2. Clipboard History

Each saved clipboard entry stores:

* Unique ID
* Text content
* Device name
* Created timestamp
* Updated timestamp
* Pinned status
* Expiration date (optional)

Actions

* Copy
* Edit
* Delete
* Pin/Unpin

---

## 3. File Sharing

Users can upload files from any browser.

Supported Features

* Drag & Drop upload
* File picker
* Multiple file upload
* Download
* Delete
* Rename
* Search files
* Copy download link
* Preview supported file types

Supported Preview Types

* Images
* PDF
* Text
* Audio
* Video
* Markdown

All other file types are downloadable.

---

## 4. Recent Files

Display:

* File name
* File size
* Uploaded by
* Upload time
* Download count (optional)

Actions

* Download
* Copy Link
* Delete
* Rename

---

## 5. QR Code

Generate a QR code pointing to the current ShareDesk URL.

Purpose

Allow users to quickly open ShareDesk on mobile devices by scanning the QR code.

---

## 6. Device Identification

On first visit, prompt for an optional device name.

Examples

* Desktop
* Office PC
* Laptop
* Android Phone
* iPhone
* Tablet

The device name is stored in browser Local Storage and attached to uploads and clipboard entries.

---

## 7. Search

Global search supporting:

* Clipboard text
* File names

Search results update instantly as the user types.

---

## 8. Authentication

### Public Mode

Anyone on the LAN can access ShareDesk.

### Password Mode

Single shared password protects the application.

Future versions may support user accounts and roles.

---

## 9. Settings

Configurable options:

* Application title
* Port
* Upload directory
* Maximum upload size
* Clipboard history limit
* File retention period
* Enable password protection
* Enable QR code
* Enable LAN-only mode
* Theme (Light/Dark/Auto)

