# REST API

## Clipboard

GET /api/clipboard

Returns clipboard history.

POST /api/clipboard

Creates a new clipboard entry.

PUT /api/clipboard/{id}

Updates an existing entry.

DELETE /api/clipboard/{id}

Deletes an entry.

---

## Files

GET /api/files

Returns uploaded files.

POST /api/files/upload

Uploads one or more files.

GET /api/files/{id}

Downloads a file.

DELETE /api/files/{id}

Deletes a file.

---

