# Design Principles

* Keep the application lightweight.
* Prioritize simplicity over complexity.
* Avoid unnecessary dependencies.
* Ensure excellent performance on low-powered home servers.
* Make every feature usable from a standard web browser.
* Default to privacy and local-network operation.
* Provide a clean, responsive interface for desktop and mobile devices.

